name: Examples of Sharpsign Asterisk

sections.text:
For example,
       #*101111
      #6*101111
      #6*101
      #6*1011
all mean the same thing: a vector of length 6 with elements 1, 0, 1, 1, 1,
and 1.
For example:
      #*         ;An empty bit-vector
